Source: gnome-shell-extension-screenshot-tool-launcher
Section: gnome
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Michael Markevich <michael@markevich.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: gnome-shell-extension-screenshot-tool-launcher
Architecture: all
Depends: gnome-shell (>= 47), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Adds a configurable action button to screenshot notifications
 GNOME Shell extension that adds a configurable action button to screenshot
 and screen recording notifications, allowing you to pass the captured file
 to an external command (e.g., swappy, gimp, wl-copy).
 .
 Supports GNOME Shell 47+.
